  <title class="- topic/title ">Changing the Comparison Column</title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">You can change the column used to
	 compare experiences. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
    <steps id="steps_DFD11CB3EDDD4DD7B368A0BBA0AC6BE3" class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
      <step id="step_BEE2F1FFB1AE4816BA58C3E97C36C3F5" class="- topic/li task/step ">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the Metrics Filter tab, change the
			 control experience used to calculate lift, then click 
			 <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">show</uicontrol> to
			 change the display. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">
          <p class="- topic/p ">
            <note class="- topic/note ">All campaigns track conversion rate, or
				  the rate of visits to your 
				  <xref href="c_About_Conversion_Mboxes.xml#concept_890181F7D16A4352A789DB06B048D58A" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local" class="- topic/xref ">conversion</xref> mbox. If you inserted a 
				  <xref href="t_Creating_a_Place_Order_Mbox.xml#task_0036D5F6C062442788BB55E872816D82" type="task" format="dita" scope="local" class="- topic/xref ">Place
					 Order</xref> mbox in your campaign, you may choose AOV, RPV or Sales as your
				  control experience. 
				</note>
          </p>
          <p class="- topic/p ">For information about the 
				<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Engagement</uicontrol> option, see 
				<xref href="c_Capturing_Engagement.xml#concept_DB31E18F26EA426EB7A87EAE16A477A5" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local" class="- topic/xref ">Capturing
				  Engagement</xref>. 
			 </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
